/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, lined with buildings on both sides, stretches out into the distance, flanked by trees that add a touch of green to the concrete jungle. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, connecting the buildings and adding a sense of dynamism to the scene. The sky above is overcast, casting a soft, diffused light over the cityscape. The colors in the image are muted, with shades of gray and green dominating the palette, reflecting the urban environment and the weather conditions.
